## Step 1 — Path Reconnaissance

### Script path issues discovered

Both v1 and v2 scripts use Path(__file__).resolve().parents[N] to find REPO_ROOT:

- archive/v1/scripts/*.py: parents[3] resolves to ai_platforms/claude_projects/ (WRONG, need parents[4])
- dev/scripts/rebuild_chapters_full.py: parents[3] resolves to ai_platforms/ (WRONG, need parents[4])
- dev/scripts/extract_examples_data.py: parents[3] resolves to ai_platforms/ (WRONG, need parents[4])

Workaround: all scripts run via exec() with REPO_ROOT patched to /Users/bojiangzhang/MyProject/sdtm-pedia

